params.markdown:
Azure AI Foundry(API Management Service)

This dashboard primarily focus on logs for Azure AI Foundry service connects via API Management Service. This dashboard contains:

- Request rate
- Error rate
- Model usage
- Latency
- LLM prompt input, Response completion

embeddableConfig.description: Plot the requests by the caller IP address.
Overall model usage by LLM models
Total tokens utilized by LLM model
Total errors for the selected time range.
Average latency for the selected time range.
Utilization by different deployments types (or SKUs) that are available at model deployment time in the Azure AI Foundry resource.
Overall average latency by LLM models
Information about the total successful or failure requests.
HTTP status code over time. Useful to track the 429 errors which is when the quota is exceeded.
